Photo:ICChina and Kazakhstan decided here Wednesday to forge a permanent comprehensive strategic partnership. The decision came as Chinese President Xi Jinping held talks with Kazakh President Kassym-Jomart Tokayev at the Great Hall of the People in Beijing. Tokayev is paying a state visit to China from Tuesday to Thursday. 
